OL,3,CRider who died at North West 200 named
OL,5,FA rider who died at the North West 200
OL,6,Fmotorcycle race has been named as
OL,7,FKamil Holan, from the Czech Republic.
OL,9,FThe 48-year-old was involved in a
OL,10,Fcrash at Station Corner in the opening
OL,11,FSuperbike qualifying session on
OL,12,FThursday.
OL,14,FThe remainder of the practice sessions
OL,15,Fwhich were scheduled for Thursday
OL,16,Fmorning took place in the evening
OL,17,Finstead of three planned races.
OL,19,FOrganisers said the family have given
OL,20,Ftheir approval for the event to
OL,21,Fcontinue.
